T1  - Does financial globalization promote risk sharing?
AU  - Kose, M. Ayhan
AU  - Prasad, Eswar S.
AU  - Terrones, Marco E.
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 89
IS  - 2
SP  - 258
